---

## Dashboard Features

The report includes the following features:

- Monthly Sales Trend Analysis
- Net Sales by Product
- Net Sales by Country
- Geographic Sales Map
- Units Sold by Country
- Interactive Country Filter (Slicer)
- Cross-filtering between visualizations
- Drill-through navigation

---

## 📈 Key Insights

The dashboard enables users to:

- Monitor monthly sales performance
- Compare product performance
- Analyze sales across different countries
- Identify regional trends and market opportunities
- Support business decisions through interactive reporting

---

